Zoubida Laayouni (amụrụ n'ụbọchị nke 5 n'ọnwa Febụwarị n'afọ 1956) bụ onye na-eme egwuregwu Moroccan lara ezumike nká bụ onye ọkachamara n'ịtụfu discus
O meriri ihe nrite asatọ na African Championships in Athletics gụnyere ihe nrite ọla edo isii.
Ihe kacha mma ya n'ihe omume ahụ bụ mita 56.94 nke e debere na Meknès na 1994
Nke a bụ ihe ndekọ mba ka dị.
